; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>That&#8217=
;s what Array Labs is building, the crazy way: the most efficient image col=
lection system that ever existed in the history of mankind. </span><strong>=
Its mission is to create a daily-refreshed, high res 3D map of Earth</stron=
g><span>.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16=
px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">To be sure, Andrew&#8217;s idea=
 for Array Labs is crazy in a lot of ways.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(=
64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">For o=
ne, the Air Force Research Lab tried to use radar to make a 3D map of the E=
